      "date": "2011-08-26 08:10:57.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n{quote}\nPatch Set 2: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on rhel/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/4866e80a-ce08-11e0-8d02-52540025f9af). Ran 11 tests. No failures.\n{quote}\n\nHi Andreas and Oleg,\n\nI just saw the sanity tests were not run by the autotest system, so sanity test 220 was not verified. It failed on the latest master branch:\n\nhttps://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/b2e62138-cfba-11e0-8d02-52540025f9af\n\nhttps://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/be1fa0bc-cf6d-11e0-8d02-52540025f9af",
